<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="MTA12">
<l>cevivāykaṇ mūkkuṭaleṉ ṟaimpulaṉuñ centī</l>
<l>puvikāṉīr viṇpūta maintu – maviyāta</l>
<l>ñāṉamum vēḷviyu nallaṟamu meṉparē</l>
<l>yēṉamāy niṉṟāṟ kiyalvu</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The five sense organs, namely ear, mouth, eye, nose, body, the five</l>
<l>elements, [namely] red fire, earth, wind, water, sky, unending</l>
<l>knowledge, sacrifice and good Dharma, they say,</l>
<l>are the nature of him who stood as a boar.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
